				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Well, I can tell you that only one low level was killed by the young ones....and as a 5th or 6th level warrior, he shouldnt have been in Oasis to begin with... The Kids werent killed...they ran to the island and depopped...A bunch of ubers chased them but lost them.  The high end event was exactly that....50 or so cookie cutter spectres along with Mom and Dad yelling at us.  I responded to the shouts on how we didnt kill the kids, and a few others joined in...We offered to show proof and find the kids but that didnt help the fact that so many people were hell bent on making Spectre Island a deserted island.  I do remember someone saying that the kids were spotted inside the tower...having never been there, I think that they were playing games.  I actually got a nice tell from a GM later, congratulating me on my roleplaying...If ya guys have any more questions, let me know.<BR>
<BR>
Sephryna<BR>
